KAYIGCULISI indlela okulandelwa ngayo amacala abucayi, aphenywa ngamaphoyisa asiteshini saseHammarsdale eMpumalanga. Lawa ngamazwi kaNdunankulu waKwaZulu-Natal, uMnuz Sihle Zikalala, ofike kungazelele muntu izolo eyohlola ukusebenza kwalesi siteshi ngaphansi komkhankaso, i-Operation Siyahlola. Ubephelezelwa nguNgqongqoshe wezokuThutha, ukuPhepha nokuXhumana koMphakathi, uNkk Peggy Nkonyeni noKhomishana wamaPhoyisa esifundazweni uLieutenant General Nhlanhla Mkhwanazi. UZikalala uthe isiteshi saseHammarsdale singesinye abakhathazekile ngaso KwaZulu-Natal, kuhlanganisa esaseNanda, eMlaza, ePlessislaer nezinye. “Kule ndawo yaseHammarsdale namaphethelo izinga lobugebengu liphezulu, ukubulawa kwabantu kuphezulu, ukudlwengula nokuhlaselwa kwabantu kuphezulu. Indlela okulandelwa ngayo la macala kayenelisi neze,” kusho uZikalala. Uthe bavumelene ngemuva kwalokhu kuhlola ukuthi uNkk Nkonyeni nomnyango babuke wonke amadodoko, ikakhulukazi lawo athinta awokubulala, ukudlwengula nokushaya ukuthi ahamba kanjani. “Sifuna ukutholaukuthi yingani liphansi izinga lokuboshwa kwabantu. Yingani ekugcineni kungekho abantu okutholakala ukuthi bayagwetshwa,” kusho uZikalala. Uthe useke waya eMgugundlovu wayohlola izinhlelo zokwakhiwa kwezindlu eMsunduzi nasesiteshini samaphoyisa KwaHlabisa nasemtholampilo wakhona. Uthe izolo bebeseMpumalanga, beyohlola indlela okusebenza ngayo isiteshi namaphoyisa aso. Nakuba enelisekile ngesibalo samaphoyisa akhona kulesi siteshi, kodwa ukhala ngokuntuleka kwezinsiza ezidingekayo ukuze kwenziwe umsebenzi ngempumelelo, kubalwa nokushoda kwezimoto. 